---
layout: base.njk
title: Tools
description: Explore SEO, content, campaign, and utility tools on UD Marketing Tools.
permalink: /tools/
---

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="eyebrow">Tools Directory</span>
    <h1>Explore practical tools for content, SEO, campaigns, and utility work.</h1>
    <p>
      Browse the full set of tools available on UD Marketing Tools. Core tools appear first, followed by secondary utility tools.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">All Tools</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Core and supporting tools in one place.</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">
        These cards are generated from shared tool data, making the tools page easier to maintain over time.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid-3">
      {% for tool in tools %}
        <article class="card card-pad lift">
          <span class="eyebrow">{{ tool.category }}</span>
          <h3>{{ tool.name }}</h3>
          <p>{{ tool.description }}</p>

          {% if tool.featured %}
            <p class="muted">Priority tool</p>
          {% else %}
            <p class="muted">Supporting utility</p>
          {% endif %}

          <div class="tool-links-row">
            <a href="{{ tool.url }}" class="btn btn-primary">{{ tool.cta }}</a>
          </div>
        </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>